data.title: Colin Mochrie & Deb McGrath — Guy MacPherson
data.meta_description: "We're both pretty amazing people so we get along really well, we travel well together. It helps. It actually gives us time to spend together, which is nice."    – Colin Mochrie    "I shamelessly pursued him. Typical of most men, he was clueless as a post."    – Deb McGrath
data.text:
"We're both pretty amazing people so we get along really well, we travel well together. It helps. It actually gives us time to spend together, which is nice."

– Colin Mochrie

"I shamelessly pursued him. Typical of most men, he was clueless as a post."

– Deb McGrath
